title: The_Killers_Day_and_Age_2008-TL
description:
The_Killers_Day_and_Age_2008-TL

The Killers' third collection of new material, 'Day And Age', is said by

frontman Brandon Flowers to be 'a continuation', of the concept used for

their second album, 'Sam's Town'.Produced by Stuart Price, who the band

came across after hecreated the 'Thin White Duke' remix of 'Mr Brightside',

'Day And Age' is the band's first original release in two years. Upon

receiving the album, MTV claimed that it had the bestcover-art of any

album ever. 'Day And Age' is preceded by the single, 'Human'.

Bitrate: 320 kbps
